('6818f27a-fe52-1e3e-fc79-54998253343e', -539, 2, NULL, NULL, '古代两河流域新巴比伦王国灭国。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2014-12-23 00:00:00', 1, '64789949-6480-311f-9478-54b0d78b2c72'),
